# ============================================
# Silicon Thermal Conductivity via NEMD (v4)
# Muller-Plathe method
# Matches Heris et al. (2022) parameters:
#   - dt = 0.5 fs, swap every 100 steps (= 50 fs)
# Usage: lmp -in in.si_thermal_v4 -var LEN 20
# ============================================

units           metal
atom_style      atomic
boundary        p p p

lattice         diamond 5.431
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 5.431 5.431 5.431
region          box block 0 6 0 6 0 ${LEN}
region          box block 0 6 0 6 0 60
create_box      1 box
Created orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (32.586 32.586 325.86)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms    1 box
